ions (tEHEL from NEx high to NEx low) and the maximum time required by the memory to free the data bus after a read access (tEHQZ): (BUSTRUN + 1) KCK_FMC period &#8805; tEHELmin and (BUSTRUN + 2)KCK_FMC period &#8805; tEHQZmax if EXTMOD = 0 (BUSTRUN + 2)KCK_FMC period &#8805; max (tEHELmin, tEHQZmax) if EXTMOD =1. ...
